Package radirius.merc.utilities.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    A Command that will do a specific task when asked in the given inputstream (by default, the console).
    CommandList
    A collection of Commands and Variables to be accessed in the given inputstream (the console by default).
    CommandThread
    A thread to be ran seperate from the library itself so that in-game freezes will not effect the console, and that the Scanner will not hang.
    Variable
    A Variable that can be referenced within the given inputstream (the console by default).
